Class Footprint

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.Footprint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Footprint
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the footprint of an agent which contains the home address (IP address and home port of the agent client that created this agent) of the agent and the IP address and port where the agent has been sent.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
